=Description=

"The Community Land Trust network in the UK connects people to information about the CLT movement, how CLTs operate, resources for and assistance in establishing a CLT,  funding options, and other CLT practitioners."

The Community Land Trust Fund ("CLT Fund")  was launched in October 2008 with the aim of assisting the development of community-led affordable housing projects; helping to build sustainable communities.

The CLT Fund provides funding and expert support to fledgling Community Land Trusts from initial feasibility – where communities are identifying a need and thinking about a solution – through to the construction of affordable homes. (http://www.cltfund.org.uk/)


